1.0.1 - Aug 02 2017
 * install.sh: The env var "PREFIX" was being ignored during installation.
 Either form was affected:
   PREFIX="/opt/bash-resume" ./install.sh
 or
   ./install.sh PREFIX="/opt/bash-resume"
 * Minor updates to README

 * Note version info in _BR_VERSION (full string, 1.0.1) and
 _BR_VERSION_{MAJOR,MINOR,PATCHLEVEL} as the split of those dots. See commit

